Text:
6 wallpapers.

Each wallpaper is provided in 800x600, 1024x768, 1280x800, 1280x1024, 1440x900, 1680x1050, 1920x1200, 2560x1600.  Minor variation in content between sizes.

Each wallpaper is the Original Show Enterprise vividly reproduced using modern-graphics, with a background of planets, rings, etc.

The Original Show Star Trek logo is prominently displayed in the middle of what would otherwise be very pretty artwork.

Still, worth the download.
